   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00341"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00957-1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb44311">San Martino di Castrozzo</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00957-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> kam am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1899-08-10" subtype="date-only"/> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb44311">San Martino di Castrozza</rs> an und dürfte die
                     Karte vorgefunden haben.</note></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb423" type="place">Tirol</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00342"/>Ich freu mich, zu denken da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Ihr
               alle bei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>a<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eid und die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chönen Tage und
               Sternennächte genießt. <rs ref="#pmb3130" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Franken<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</hi></rs> freut<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr auf <rs ref="#pmb13055" type="person">Wa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ermann</rs>. Ich
               erbitte von <rs ref="#pmb10863" type="person">Richard</rs> noch nähere Nachrichten wo
               er <date>13<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi></date> bis <date>16<hi rend="superscript">ten</hi></date> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t, eben<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o von Ihnen</p><p><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40256" type="place">Alt-Aussee Gasthaus Bru<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>thaler</rs></hi>.</p><p>Bin<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr erholt und wohl.</p><closer>Herzlich Euer<lb/><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
